        <mxCell id="step-retrieve" value="&lt;b&gt;2. Hybrid Retrieve&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Dense (cosine) top-30&lt;br&gt;• Lexical (LIKE) top-30&lt;br&gt;• RRF fusion → top-K&lt;br&gt;• Filters: company, date&lt;br&gt;• Recency boost" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=11;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=6" vertex="1" parent="1">
